================================================================================

When you understand all above content, respond EXACTLY:

SYSTEM READY.

Workspace: [your-workspace-name or "to-be-determined"]
Security: Understood (PUBLIC repo, no credentials)
Focus: [CURRENT_FOCUS.md | status.md | will-check]
Ready: [describe what you're ready to do OR questions you have]

